task.summary:
Added warning boxes for the following user cases:
*When you roll the dice, you're no longer allowed to de-select it. *When you click on a dice before rolling, you're no longer allowed to actually select it.
Got it working again, working on getting the RoundPoints label to work when we click on a dice.
roundPoints label now functions. Not sure why it's just ADDING to the round points and not subtracting if we remove a hold :/
roundPoints now tallies appropriately and will farkle if you haven't obtained any roundPoints when you roll.
It's working well, but needs bankpoints debug as well as roundpoints.
Scoring system works now. Everything is completed with the program. I'll make this the new master that we can branch from and test.
